survey.music_making: I'm a percussionist that went to college for music. I've been playing percussion since I was 7. I started out on piano for that and played for about 5 years.
survey.activities: Driving and at work when I need to concentrate.
survey.other_genres: Nothing else that I can think of.
survey.habit_change: My likes and interests have only gotten bigger! I love finding new bands that I've missed and new bands that are just coming out with stuff. Music is a huge part of my life!
